{"tid":1217605,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律jj]其實暴動罪點計","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:52:04.000Z","uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"966a6e643763f2ed848cf647ac999eb113d17e21","tid":1217605,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>學術討論</strong><br />\n其實界定暴動又係警方<br />\n佢又唔洗現場宣布或者電視公布<br />\n咁點介定係入暴動定非法集會？<br />\n如果有人去唱聖詩<br />\n唔知金鐘地方比人定性做暴動<br />\n比人拉咗佢又係暴動？<br />\n唔係應該宣布咗<br />\n比啲覺得唔想參與嘅人離開現場先㗎咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打個比方說<br />\n如果69朝早遊行拉咗人<br />\n佢忽然話69遊行係暴動都可以改charge暴動罪㗎？<br />\n<br />\nSorry真係唔識法律<br />\n<br />\n<strong>學術討論</strong>"},{"pid":"ae230b0dc6be86ec5cb077263c1d47327cbf842a","tid":1217605,"uid":71977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"暴動<br />\n(1)如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動。  (由1970年第31號第12條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n(2)任何人參與暴動，即犯暴動罪 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁10年；及<br />\n(b)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁5年。"},{"pid":"172051d67fd9c192b6d08e5c4e4fa8e2dc86ab05","tid":1217605,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"海外港人支援流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204022</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/港人海外支援-Global-Support-for-Hongkongese-334803087194135/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-Global-Support-for-Hongkongese-334803087194135%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=0a1704ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/港人海外支援-Global-Support-for-Hongkongese-334803087194135/</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram:<br />\n@hkglobalsupport"},{"pid":"5daed239af12d05231f65a0e895ee12eae67ef2c","tid":1217605,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae230b